</h2><p><strong>連接題目主機</strong></p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-SHELL" data-lang="SHELL"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">#題目提供連線方法</span>
